{"tid":1715711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將所有學校既枱枱凳凳搬晒出馬路，掉晒出街","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T10:25:54.000Z","uid":131264,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"afffcc322cd292e43147cfaa4833775c3a2609ac","tid":1715711,"uid":131264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:05:57.000Z","msg":"全部<br />\n今晚<br />\n<br />\n攞去燒又好，做路障都好<br />\n搬晒出去<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講其他廢話<br />\n搬枱搬凳你都唔制<br />\n<br />\n人地隨時會開火屠殺中大啲學生<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">搬枱搬凳渣屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你有無諗過如果中大真係淪陷<br />\n黑警就等於佔領左一個易守難攻既點<br />\n呢件事一發生，黑警落街<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屠殺市民</span>，仲可以點樣反抗？<br />\n佢將啲物資，裝備全部擺晒係中大，成個戰略基地咁<br />\n<br />\n有無諗過黑警透過政府拎晒你地啲資料<br />\n只係因為依家打緊仗，唔得閒慢慢捉<br />\n到場仗真係輸左果陣，你地邊個接觸過關於呢場運動既野<br />\n全部拉鳩晒佢，係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不論藍黃</span>呀<br />\n依家人地係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">清洗我地香港人</span>呀<br />\n好快就會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入民居拉鳩晒你地</span><br />\n搬枱搬凳你都唔制，拉鳩晒你地囉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拉鳩晒你地呀</span><br />\n<br />\n遲下黑警仲會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當街強姦女仔</span><br />\n你信唔信丫？<br />\n你緊係唔信啦，點會去到咁嚴重呀<br />\n你自己依家行落街望下啲港豬有幾撚多<br />\n你問你自己，如果咁既畫面真係出面係條街到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有幾多人會埋去阻止？</span><br />\n其實你自己已經好撚清楚個答案<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係你信唔信既問題<br />\n係件事都未發生，個社會已經講左答案畀你知</span><br />\n咁你係咪一定要等到件事發生左先相信呀？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遲撚晒喇屌你老母</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">將所有學校既枱枱凳凳搬晒出馬路，掉晒出街<br />\n全部<br />\n今晚</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c6a8573a94920920678295c8cf9f80e31e471c6","tid":1715711,"uid":71952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:06:39.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"d01a3f21043977baf9de88416e14c5e0fe8918c7","tid":1715711,"uid":204692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:07:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1e99d8ea59bc14f9114c7e0e2e3d1777b770cca","tid":1715711,"uid":131264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b9a05b6a24e1f29501e58dd4460d14c03fe4999","tid":1715711,"uid":131264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:43:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95e2238d14fd3ba9f1a5cc8d2c04878570eed2e5","tid":1715711,"uid":67152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebbb873d307c977b60bcc16bb852f25efecbf9c","tid":1715711,"uid":131264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:57:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"032d265ef350a2c4a343ecaa010bf8323176f4bc","tid":1715711,"uid":131264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e2238d14fd3ba9f1a5cc8d2c04878570eed2e5","tid":1715711,"uid":67152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:58:16.000Z","msg":"我自己都著手準備緊<br />\n由佢啦<br />\n有第一個人做出來自然會有人跟<br />\n依家出post叫人點點點，無人理先正路"},{"pid":"5ac27432ffbbb6dd009c3f974b8f392ed1f7f041","tid":1715711,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:58:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d4ffdae078a62564136813a467763d7e7c27fac","tid":1715711,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dee7fb4c39ac71eb8564a2b32c0ee2d7e6b1710e","tid":1715711,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"火魔不足<br />\n幫到手嘅運上去"},{"pid":"35e3d765a193c45fcd0e2db050de237ec51f54a6","tid":1715711,"uid":131264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:03:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"052b52fe902758ae6c78562638aee4489a8f5686","tid":1